{
  "stem": "23090.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as a child, that's another impression that you heard that whistling of a bomb, and you don't-- you never know when and how close it's going to get to you.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was living on the day-- drawn shades.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And lights had to be off during the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you were permitted only to use lights at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Lights-- lights were comprised of maybe two or three bulbs in the-- in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you had to draw your shades, and there better not be any cracks or any, any visibility throughout.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you were just kind of growing in that environment, and that environment was a scary, scary, terrible environment for a young child to be in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a way, I was being prepared, in my own little mind, to cope with it, because your mother and your father couldn't continue to say to you well, don't worry, don't worry, because there was something to worry.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and how far can you protect and shield?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as you grow up, you kind of form your own scaredness and your own way of existing and your own way of coping with it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Playing with your friends becomes secondary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now you're starting to be a little more hungry, and there's a little less food available.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the things that you had prior is now not so available.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're now in that mode and that-- on the road of existing rather than living.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And things don't get better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just get worse, progressively worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] now we don't have food, now we rationed, this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can we-- can we stay a little bit longer before the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
